reviewText: Interesting but not really for a haunted house

As others that posted a review.  I was very disappointed with this video.  There is only creepy music playing throughout with snippets of old haunt films.  There are no instructions or 'how to' sections throughout the entire video.  The title is misleading.
I thought this was a movie BUT found out it's just scary sound's so if you think this IS a movie like I did don't buy this BUT if you want scary sound's for Halloween then this IS for you.
Me and my little Grand daughter really enjoyed this video for HalloweenNice music
Good scary stuff for all ages. Great montage of Halloween music and scary movie clip
Really neat to have playing in the background for a Halloween party.
It's cool but the scenes don't last long enough. They are meant to be like those Fireplace scene videos made for Christmas. But because they flip the scenes too fast the scare is just not there.
One star is too many, but you can't go lower.
